"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/850975","Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","false","2018-03-07","<p>The Department has made no such estimate.</p><p> </p><p> </p>","Burton","Andrew Griffiths","130178 ; 130179","2018-03-07T13:54:14.367Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/850975/answer","Biography information for Andrew Griffiths","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/850975/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/850975/answer",,,,,,,,"201","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy","2018-02-27","Small Businesses: Billing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy, what estimate his Department has made of the level of debt accrued by SMEs as a result of late payments.","false","Biography information for Dr Matthew Offord","Hendon","Dr Matthew Offord","130177"
